# KOMPAK Apps — Project Overview

## Stack

- Vue 3.5 Composition API + Vite 6 + TypeScript + Tailwind 4
- Leaflet + leaflet.markercluster (imperatif, bukan react-leaflet)
- Ikon: `lucide-vue-next`

## Entry & shell

- Entry: `src/main.ts` → `src/App.vue`
- Navigasi: view-switcher via `ref` di App — **bukan** Vue Router
- Views: `home` | `map` | `producer-dashboard` | `coop-dashboard` | `add-product` | `entity-detail`
- Navigasi antar view: `emit('navigate', view, data?)`

## Struktur folder

```
src/
  App.vue              # shell + sidebar + view switcher
  components/          # halaman fitur (LandingPage, MapView, …)
  components/ui/     # primitif UI (Button, Tabs, Sidebar*, …)
  composables/         # logic reusable (useInView, …)
  styles/              # globals.css tokens, tailwind, fonts
```

## Import

- Alias `@/` → `src/` (contoh: `import { Button } from '@/components/ui'`)

## Larangan

- Jangan reintroduksi React, `@figma/astraui*`, atau dependency React boilerplate
- Jangan tambah Vue Router/Pinia kecuali diminta eksplisit

## Konten

- Copy UI dalam Bahasa Indonesia
